- 🔲 **Semantic duplicate detection** — LLM identifies records that are the same entity despite different formatting
- 🔲 **Data entry error detection** — LLM distinguishes typos from valid rare values
- 🔲 **Impossible value reasoning** — contextual understanding beyond simple range rules

### 8.3 Smart Feature Engineering 🤖
- 🔲 **AI feature suggestion** — LM Studio proposes domain-relevant features from column context
- 🔲 **Recency / seasonality feature proposals** — AI identifies temporal patterns worth encoding
- 🔲 **Interaction feature suggestion** — AI recommends meaningful feature interactions (e.g., `debt_ratio × income`)
